00:25:52.336 --> 00:25:53.469
<v ->I wish I could tell you the countries,</v>

711
00:25:53.469 --> 00:25:55.580
I, I know in Russia it is actually a holiday,

712
00:25:55.580 --> 00:25:57.725
'cause we, but, one year, we heard this lovely note

713
00:25:57.725 --> 00:25:59.048
from a woman who said,

714
00:25:59.048 --> 00:26:00.604
"thank you so much for Gather the Women.

715
00:26:00.604 --> 00:26:03.016
"Usually on International Women's Day,

716
00:26:03.016 --> 00:26:04.850
"the men bring us roses on Monday

