00:26:07.911 --> 00:26:10.331
"This year we came together as women

719
00:26:10.331 --> 00:26:13.415
"and, and shared our stories and our support,

720
00:26:13.415 --> 00:26:15.324
"and it was different, so we thank you."

721
00:26:15.324 --> 00:26:18.289
And it was just, it was a lovely, lovely comment

722
00:26:18.289 --> 00:26:20.454
for the difference that it made

