00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:24.720
It is, actually, International Women's Day

725
00:26:24.720 --> 00:26:27.302
has been around a very, very, very long time.

726
00:26:27.302 --> 00:26:30.257
I remember it being reinitiated, if you will,

727
00:26:30.257 --> 00:26:33.603
it 1975 at the United Nations

728
00:26:33.603 --> 00:26:37.478
First World Conference in Mexico City.

729
00:26:37.478 --> 00:26:40.559
And, and as I said, some countries have taken to it,

730
00:26:40.559 --> 00:26:41.702
and some haven't.

731
00:26:41.702 --> 00:26:43.931
This one is one, this country is one in which

732
00:26:43.931 --> 00:26:46.756
I, I wish we could say we, we hear more about it

733
00:26:46.756 --> 00:26:47.995
and we don't.

734
00:26:47.995 --> 00:26:49.636
And when we do hear about it in this country

735
00:26:49.636 --> 00:26:52.197
it is very often looking at our history

736
00:26:52.197 --> 00:26:57.197
and just honoring what has been done by women.

737
00:26:57.957 --> 00:27:01.092
I think we bring something different to it.

738
00:27:01.092 --> 00:27:03.546
And what I believe we bring to it is,

739
00:27:03.546 --> 00:27:06.286
is making it very current.

740
00:27:06.286 --> 00:27:09.145
And also that it is our intention

741
00:27:09.145 --> 00:27:10.702
when we ask women to come together

742
00:27:10.702 --> 00:27:13.229
for International Women's Day, to,

743
00:27:13.229 --> 00:27:17.038
to basically invite the future, if you will,

744
00:27:17.038 --> 00:27:19.565
within each women, to inspire, to connect,

745
00:27:19.565 --> 00:27:23.331
to plug them in to all the various activities

746
00:27:23.331 --> 00:27:24.771
that they could be involved in,

747
00:27:24.771 --> 00:27:26.563
and to encourage them.

748
00:27:26.563 --> 00:27:27.907
To create their own.

749
00:27:27.907 --> 00:27:31.180
We also bring to it, I believe a spiritual perspective,

750
00:27:31.180 --> 00:27:34.242
which is that we, we're not religious per se

751
00:27:34.242 --> 00:27:38.817
and we honor all cross sections of, of spirituality.

752
00:27:38.817 --> 00:27:41.421
But we also encourage women to listen to their hearts

753
00:27:41.421 --> 00:27:43.041
and listen to spirit.

754
00:27:43.041 --> 00:27:44.523
And ask themselves, you know,

755
00:27:44.523 --> 00:27:45.739
where am I coming from on this,

756
00:27:45.739 --> 00:27:48.055
am I, why am I angry?

757
00:27:48.055 --> 00:27:49.707
Or, where am I coming from on this,

758
00:27:49.707 --> 00:27:51.893
what is motivating me in this moment?

759
00:27:51.893 --> 00:27:54.966
Is it my agenda or is it my service to others?

760
00:27:54.966 --> 00:27:57.889
And so we continually ask women to check in.

