781
00:28:36.189 --> 00:28:39.069
it's almost like going back to the 50s and 60s for us,

782
00:28:39.069 --> 00:28:42.536
they are on the streets asking for their rights as women.

783
00:28:42.536 --> 00:28:44.786
Rights, basic rights as women.

